Escalade Inc.

Escalade, Incorporated (Escalade) is a quality manufacturer and distributor of sporting goods through our wholly owned subsidiary Escalade Sports. Escalade delivers
                outstanding products, superior customer service and consistent shareholder value.
                
Sporting Goods


Headquartered in Evansville, Indiana, Escalade Sports manufactures, imports, and distributes widely recognized sporting goods brands in basketball goals, archery, indoor and outdoor game recreation and fitness products through major sporting goods retailers, specialty dealers, key on-line retailers, traditional department stores and mass merchants. Escalade is a leader in table tennis tables, residential in-ground basketball goals and in archery bows. Some of the Company’s most recognized brands, owned or distributed, include: 


Product Segment
Brand Names


Archery
Bear Archery®, Trophy Ridge®, Whisker Biscuit®, Cajun Bowfishing™


Table Tennis
STIGA®, Ping-Pong®, Prince®


Basketball Goals
Goalrilla™, Goaliath®, Silverback®, Hoopstar™, Goalsetter®


Play Systems
Woodplay®, ChildLife®


Fitness
The STEP®, USWeight™, Lifeline®, Kettleworx®, Natural Fitness™, PER4M®


Game Tables (Hockey and Soccer)
Atomic®, American Legend®, Redline®, Triumph™


Billiards Accessories
Mizerak®, Minnesota Fats®, Lucasi®, PureX®, Rage®, Players®


Darting
Unicorn®, Accudart®, Arachnid®, Nodor®, Winmau®


Outdoor Games
Zume Games®, Pickleball Now, Onix®, Viva Sol®, Triumph™







©  Escalade Inc. All rights reserved.






Ideas Submission | Escalade IncHomeOverviewCompany HistoryVision/Mission StatementOfficers & DirectorsCorporate GovernanceBrandsInvestor RelationsStock QuotePresident's MessageReports & FilingsOther InformationDisclaimerCorporate DevelopmentNew IdeasUnsolicited Idea Submission PolicyTerms of SubmissionContactNew IdeasWe're seeking great ideas within the sporting goods and outdoor recreation markets.As a leader in the sporting goods and outdoor recreation markets, Escalade Inc. knows that partnering is a basis for success.  We believe users of sporting goods and outdoor recreation products are some of the most important innovators in the market.We're looking for ways to bring new ideas to the market and seek that expertise developed by passionate users of sporting goods and outdoor recreation products. Do you have an idea for a product or service to share with Escalade? We would appreciate hearing from you to explore the opportunity to bring your idea to life.To share your ideas with us, you must first read and agree to our Unsolicited Idea Submission Policy and Terms of Submission.We are also interrested in exploring opportunites through mergers, acquisitions, joint ventures, partnerships and licensing agreements to facilitate our long-term growth objectives. Specifically, we focus on strategic, bolt-on, and new platform opportunities that help enhance or expand our business and geographic footprint. If you would like to discuss any potential opportunities with us, please visit our Corporate Development web page.©  Escalade Inc. All rights reserved.Mission Statement | Overview | Escalade IncHomeOverviewCompany HistoryVision/Mission StatementOfficers & DirectorsCorporate GovernanceBrandsInvestor RelationsStock QuotePresident's MessageReports & FilingsOther InformationDisclaimerCorporate DevelopmentNew IdeasUnsolicited Idea Submission PolicyTerms of SubmissionContactMission & VisionStatement of Corporate BeliefsIt is our belief that in order to achieve our full potential, both as individuals and as a corporation, we must meet our responsibility to all those associated with our business; including our community and country.We must treat our employees with fairness, always respecting the dignity of the individual, and provide a clean, safe environment.We must recognize that our customers are of utmost importance.We must treat our best suppliers as partners.We must maintain and enhance the intrinsic value of our shareholders' assets through an attitude of constant growth and improvement.We must insure that open communications exist throughout our business environment.We must provide a sense of security in return for good performance to all those associated with our business.We must demand excellence, recognize it, and reward it.We must be totally committed to producing high quality products at the fairest prices. And while our fiscal responsibility is to make a sound profit, we must do so without harming the community or the environment.If we strive to meet our responsibilities, if we devote our efforts toward that end, we will be able to set ambitious goals and attain them ... we will be able to surpass former accomplishments, and reach even higher.We will be successful ... as individuals and as a corporation.Employee PledgeWe, the employees of Escalade, Incorporated and its subsidiaries, will produce products and deliver services that meet or exceed our customer's expectations.We will price these goods and services fairly.We will continually improve our products and services, always listening to our customers.We will strive to keep every single promise we make.©  Escalade Inc. All rights reserved.Stock Quote | Investor Relations | Escalade IncHomeOverviewCompany HistoryVision/Mission StatementOfficers & DirectorsCorporate GovernanceBrandsInvestor RelationsStock QuotePresident's MessageReports & FilingsOther InformationDisclaimerCorporate DevelopmentNew IdeasUnsolicited Idea Submission PolicyTerms of SubmissionContactStock QuoteThe Company's stock is publicly traded on NASDAQ under the symbol ESCA. The information contained in this link is maintained by a third party and is not controlled by the Company. Accordingly, the Company assumes no responsibility for the accuracy or timeliness of the information presented by the third party web site. ©  Escalade Inc. All rights reserved.

