Ideas Submission | Escalade IncHomeOverviewCompany HistoryVision/Mission StatementOfficers & DirectorsCorporate GovernanceBrandsInvestor RelationsStock QuotePresident's MessageReports & FilingsOther InformationDisclaimerCorporate DevelopmentNew IdeasUnsolicited Idea Submission PolicyTerms of SubmissionContactNew IdeasWe're seeking great ideas within the sporting goods and outdoor recreation markets.As a leader in the sporting goods and outdoor recreation markets, Escalade Inc. knows that partnering is a basis for success.  We believe users of sporting goods and outdoor recreation products are some of the most important innovators in the market.We're looking for ways to bring new ideas to the market and seek that expertise developed by passionate users of sporting goods and outdoor recreation products. Do you have an idea for a product or service to share with Escalade? We would appreciate hearing from you to explore the opportunity to bring your idea to life.To share your ideas with us, you must first read and agree to our Unsolicited Idea Submission Policy and Terms of Submission.We are also interrested in exploring opportunites through mergers, acquisitions, joint ventures, partnerships and licensing agreements to facilitate our long-term growth objectives. Specifically, we focus on strategic, bolt-on, and new platform opportunities that help enhance or expand our business and geographic footprint. If you would like to discuss any potential opportunities with us, please visit our Corporate Development web page.©  Escalade Inc. All rights reserved.



